name: ɐʇnɹƃ
description: Located on an island Ilha do Mel, Brazil, this cave is called "Gruta das Encantadas". I took this photo on a 35mm analog camera and gave it a certain movement, reminiscent of the sea and its shells behind.  This island is a beatufiul and peacefull place to be, without access to cars, the only access is by boat. I miss traveling so much, it's one of my favourite things in life... I wish i could see the world again...
